OL,3,CGraduates accuse government of acting
OL,4,Clike 'loan sharks' over student debt
OL,6,FMembers of the National Union of
OL,7,FStudents (NUS) have urged the
OL,8,FChancellor not to "act like a loan
OL,9,Fshark" over student debt as they
OL,10,Fstaged a protest outside parliament.
OL,12,FGraduates also called for her to
OL,13,Freverse her decision to freeze the
OL,14,Frepayment threshold for Plan 2 student
OL,15,Floans for the next three years.
OL,17,FIn the wake of Wednesday's protest,
OL,18,FLabour's deputy leader Lucy Powell
OL,19,Fcriticised "egregious" interest rates
OL,20,Fon student loans, despite Chancellor
OL,21,FRachel Reeves defending the system.
