OL,3,CGraduates accuse government of acting
OL,4,Clike 'loan sharks' over student debt
OL,6,FPowell said repayments for some
OL,7,Fgraduates felt "unfair" and "endless",
OL,8,Fbut she could not promise action would
OL,9,Fbe taken "in the near term", citing
OL,10,Fthe potential costs to government.
OL,12,FRecent polling suggested the majority
OL,13,Fof graduates disagree with the maximum
OL,14,Fstudent loan interest. Some 84% of
OL,15,F3,209 people surveyed by campaign
OL,16,Fgroup Organise said a "fairer" system
OL,17,Fwould also influence how they voted.
