OL,3,CGraduates accuse government of acting
OL,4,Clike 'loan sharks' over student debt
OL,6,FIn November's budget, Ms Reeves
OL,7,Fannounced plans to freeze the
OL,8,Fthreshold at which Plan 2 student
OL,9,Floans are paid back for three years at
OL,10,F#29,385. The Chancellor insisted the
OL,11,Fsystem is "fair" and "reasonable"
OL,12,Fafter criticism of the move.
OL,14,FInterest is charged on Plan 2 loans at
OL,15,Fthe rate of Retail Prices Index (RPI)
OL,16,Finflation and up to 3% depending on
OL,17,Fhow much a graduate earns. The maximum
OL,18,Finterest is currently 6.2% because the
OL,19,Frate of inflation is at 3.2% as of
OL,20,FSeptember 2025.
