OL,3,CGraduates accuse government of acting
OL,4,Clike 'loan sharks' over student debt
OL,6,FAt the autumn budget, the government
OL,7,Fannounced the repayment threshold for
OL,8,FPlan 2 loans, which is set to rise to
OL,9,F#29,385 in April 2026, will be frozen
OL,10,Ffor three years, which will mean more
OL,11,Fgraduates will start making repayments
OL,12,Fearlier than they would have if the
OL,13,Fthreshold increased with inflation.
OL,15,FPlan 2 loans were issued to English
OL,16,Fstudents who started their
OL,17,Fundergraduate courses between 2012/13
OL,18,Fand 2022/23.
