OL,6,F"I think, to be fair, what Rachel was
OL,7,Fprobably talking about was more in the
OL,8,Fgenerality, which is: is it fair that
OL,9,Fgraduates make a contribution towards
OL,10,Ftheir education? Because obviously, as
OL,11,Fgraduates in general, we do earn a lot
OL,12,Fmore money over our lifetime.
OL,14,F"And I think the general principle is
OL,15,Ffair, but I do accept absolutely that
OL,16,Fthere are issues around this plan too,
OL,17,Fand the plus 3%, that particularly is
OL,18,Fparticularly egregious, in my humble
OL,19,Fopinion."
