OL,3,CGraduates accuse government of acting
OL,4,Clike 'loan sharks' over student debt
OL,6,FMs Powell said she had spoken to the
OL,7,FChancellor and other ministers about
OL,8,Fthe loans and believed Ms Reeves had
OL,9,Fbeen speaking in general terms when
OL,10,Fshe defended the system.
OL,12,FBut she added she could not "promise
OL,13,Fthat that means action would be taken
OL,14,Fin the near-term" because "the way
OL,15,Fthese sort of financial packages work,
OL,16,Fyou know, it actually works out quite
OL,17,Fexpensive for the government to write
OL,18,Foff student debts because it counts
OL,19,Ffor the one year that you do it".
